Text:
Not *Studster*, 

Keith Jarrett - The Kรถln Concert (Studio Master) [FLAC]

Fucking TPB!

^^^^ Ha! Well, depending on your perspective Mr. Jarrett could be a "studster" too on the piano.

It coulda been worse.

Thanks for this....

Just wanted to thank you for the Studio Master upload. Found a couple of these on the net and they are excellent quality.

Any more ECM releases would be very much appreciated.

Looking forward to giving you a Quality:+ when I had a listen.

I just realized that my ECM CD of "The Kรถln Concert" is its first 1984 digital incarnation when timing for the new format was still an issue, and the encore (otherwise known as "Part 2 c") was lopped off.  Thanks so much for this: now I can replace my inferior CD which replaced a well-worn vinyl copy of the complete concert!
